Dayton Power & Light Co Overview



Website:

www.dplinc.com

Locations:


                                                             Aberdeen, OH 

                                                
& 7 other cities



Employees:
330




Founded:
N/A
CEO:
N/A
Industry:

Electric Services



Revenue:
$678,243,150





                                            The headquarters of Dayton Power & Light Co, an electric services company, are located at Aberdeen, OH. It has an annual revenue of $678.2 million and employs 330 people. For its niche allure, Dayton Power & Light Co is receiving quite the notice. A CEO manages the company.
                                        









