Zip:











One-time payments using eBill are also available.




		Simplify Your Life with DP&L E-Bill

		Save time and the environment when you go paperless with DP&L E-Bill. You’ll receive an email when your bill is ready to view and pay each month. Other convenient features available through DP&L E-Bill include:  


			Intuitive, mobile-friendly design

			Billing and payment notifications available by email and text

			Schedule payments in advance

			Receive your bill as a PDF email attachment

			Easy-to-use Automatic Payment option


		…and more! Get more details on DP&L E-Bill here.

		Set Up is Fast and Simple

		DP&L E-Bill is available on MyDP&L. Just create a MyDP&L profile, then select the E-Bill Enroll link on the bottom of Account Summary to sign up! Once you’re set up, you’ll stop receiving a paper bill.

		Please note, if you are a Summary Bill customer, you will continue to receive a paper copy of the detailed billing statement that includes each of your accounts.
Back to Top


		Pay Online or Over the Phone with Speedpay

		A convenient way to pay your bill without writing a check is through Speedpay. When you access the Speedpay website or call the Speedpay automated phone line, you can make an electronic payment to your DP&L bill using your bank account, ATM/debit card, Visa, MasterCard or Discover.

		Two easy ways to use Speedpay


Pay online

			Call 866-305-3095


		All online and phone payments are processed through Western Union Speedpay, an independent service provider. Payments made through the Speedpay option Monday- Friday before 7 p.m. Eastern Standard Time will post to your account the next business day.

Back to Top

		MyDP&L

		Access DP&L E-Bill, review your account summary and pay your bill online when you sign into MyDP&L. You can also view and download up to 24 months of payment history. Learn more.

Back to Top












